title: 多人机MOD联机报错
author: liboyang31202
txt_content:
服务端开服正常无报错，客户端无报错
1.0.1-2,DynamicLights_mobEquipment@1.0.8,NEIAddons|AppEng@1.12.14.40,FML@7.10.99.99,NotEnoughItems@1.0.5.120,NEIAddons|Botany@1.12.14.40,MouseTweaks@2.4.4,IC2@2.2.828-experimental,Baubles@1.0.1.10,neiintegration@1.1.1,Mantle@1.7.10-0.3.2.jenkins191,LunatriusCore@1.1.2.21,DynamicLights_creepers@1.0.4,enchvil@1.0,DynamicLights_thePlayer@1.1.4,NEIAddons|Developer@1.12.14.40,DynamicLights_floodLights@1.0.2,Forge@10.13.4.1614,MovingWorld@1.7.10-1.8.1,bspkrsCore@6.15,ChestTransporter@2.0.6

replies.author: MIKAZE3
replies.txt_content: 客户端缺少服务端运行的这个MOD必须保证服务端有的MOD客户端必须有

replies.author: 恋
replies.txt_content: 这个应该是客户端缺少MOD  你把服务端的FlabsBF4.1.2复制进客户端的MOD文件夹 重启游戏 再进入即可

replies.author: 【捣蛋】
replies.txt_content:
[23:30:19] [Netty IO #8/信息] [FML]: Attempting connection with missing mods [FLabsBF] at CLIENT
客户端缺少一个叫[FLabsBF]的Mod
装上就可以了
